name: Awwww, Cannot Get Your Ship Out (V)
Lore: '''Listen, friend, we didn''t mean to land in that puddle, and if we could get our ship out, we would, but we can''t so why don''t you just...''',
Text: 'If opponent just drew a starship or vehicle for destiny, deploy on table, and stack that card here. Opponent may place a card (your choice) from your Lost Pile into your hand to place this Effect (and stacked cards) into owner''s Used Pile.',
